e":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:37:13.000Z","msg":"最好樓價都新彊化<br />\n全國最平呀<br />\n三千一坪都有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0949e2d2961365342a064e7356d7656a37514f4","tid":2028180,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76523ba023db93d75765013cab785d8da0570418","tid":2028180,"uid":327622,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:39:08.000Z","msg":"海洋公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30814cdcaf652f136f2f7438a8593fa95d72dca","tid":2028180,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76523ba023db93d75765013cab785d8da0570418","tid":2028180,"uid":327622,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:40:09.000Z","msg":"送中"},{"pid":"d7988db72b03baa885a671d6c379a46a45f30bae","tid":2028180,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:43:17.000Z","msg":"新疆嶺起好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562f89541b140af659791200056dcb11055ec8d8","tid":2028180,"uid":179409,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:48:43.000Z","msg":"打壓應該由2009年七五事件開始<br />\n當年廣東工廠有個支那妹<br />\n自稱俾維族人強姦（事後證實係假）<br />\n令有班支那人去搵維族人尋仇<br />\n結果打死咗幾個維族人<br />\n但政府包庇打死人嘅支那人<br />\n呢件事激起咗好多維族人憤怒<br />\n支那各地發起好多次遊行示威<br />\n支共當然用一貫口吻<br />\n話係外國勢力煽動<br />\n跟住公安開始襲擊示威者<br />\n示威者由和平遊行<br />\n演變成勇武抗爭（激過香港十倍，有部分示威者係嬲到見漢人就打）<br />\n最後俾支共定性為「恐怖活動」<br />\n公安開始殺人<br />\n然後封網、大圍捕、搞電子監視<br />\n維族人從此再無自由<br />\n過程係咪好熟悉呢？"},{"pid":"a299e76a2917b2173eb93a0e0d742365a5e49b12","tid":2028180,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:53:03.000Z","msg":"早幾個月cctv出左套紀錄片講新疆<br />\n而家出套片講香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n將新疆人講成係恐怖分子<br />\n有異曲同工之處"},{"pid":"9345264fabe333fe2a660f75d4e3faeb2abddd05","tid":2028180,"uid":151256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:01:40.000Z","msg":"香港應該唔會變新疆<br />\n<br />\n最多都係澳門"},{"pid":"17e3a083876acadd5ca3f3f041fd3aaf67c0f334","tid":2028180,"uid":149435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9345264fabe333fe2a660f75d4e3faeb2abddd05","tid":2028180,"uid":151256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:01:40.000Z","msg":"香港應該唔會變新疆<br />\n<br />\n最多都係澳門"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:46:49.000Z","msg":"好難講 澳豬唔會反抗"},{"pid":"41ff2c44aebe24eb69ddc5da61a02bdcd164329f","tid":2028180,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:48:09.000Z","msg":"係東突厥，唔係新疆"},{"pid":"91f13107065d063e02565095769f1ce4742bef3a","tid":2028180,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6aa12b38c597117c044df4d5f0d2c32332a1ef6","tid":2028180,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76523ba023db93d75765013cab785d8da0570418","tid":2028180,"uid":327622,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:34:19.000Z","msg":"捉晒過格黎深圳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:56:38.000Z","msg":"深圳都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能要東莞惠洲，大灣區見"}]}